<para>LoRa data-rate. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This enumeration represents the data rate of a LoRa signal, expressed as a Spreading Factor (SF).</para>
<para>The Spreading Factor determines how many chirps are used to encode each symbol (2^SF chips per symbol). Higher values result in lower data rates but increased range and robustness. </para>
