<para>Receive packets continuously under the configuration previously setup by <ref refid="group__lora__interface_1gad7c6c516d2d0e023da952666d3f8decb" kindref="member">lora_config</ref>.</para>
<para>Reception is cancelled by calling this function again with <computeroutput>cb</computeroutput> = NULL. This can be done within the callback handler.</para>
