        <briefdescription>
<para>Perform Channel Activity Detection asynchronously. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Starts a single CAD operation using the CAD parameters from <ref refid="group__lora__interface_1gad7c6c516d2d0e023da952666d3f8decb" kindref="member">lora_config</ref>. When complete, invokes <computeroutput>cb</computeroutput> with the result.</para>
